===Etymology 1===
From {{etyl|enm|en}} {{m|enm|gaffe||a hook}} + {{m|en|-er}}. The natural lighting on early film sets was adjusted by opening and closing flaps in the tent cloths, called gaff cloths or gaff flaps.

